<title>Lal Isu Galthuom</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gitloh sepaih gal nicheng I do zing ui .
 Thih theihna gu manga ei do chun;
 Ka gim ten ta a,
 Lal Isun A galthuom ei hun piek nung chun,
 Ngam takin ka delh kit thei zel ie.

[V2]
 Vang ei pie zel in tin,
 Ka gin chu gitloh huih in mut mahleh ling diek lo
 A det muncham suongpi sang inle.

[V3]
 2. Lau kiu zuonzel un gitloh thilbawl theihna,
 Belam No Lal sepaih nang zolo;
 Gitloh, thihna chun,
 I malam vannim le a vak kit zo tai,
 Zion khawpi a lang en tiem u.

[V4]
 3. Kidona lopi Na hun tiem tun sakin,
 Lal Isu, Mikael sawl dawkin;
 Setan chu man hen,
 Sepaih hawn gal zawh leh han kal ngaklah ui;
 Gehen Lal gilo dogal ai in.

[V5]
 4. Na angsung muonna tuhin chu ka tung tai,
 Pakna la thang suok hen lei leh van;
 Mi cheng cheng kawmah,
 Gitloh thihna thima um ei hukdawk tai;
 Ngaih man a um ka paupih Lalpa.</lyrics>
</song>